text: Bhuwan Bahadur Sunar is a politician from Nepal who belongs to the Communist Party of Nepal (Maoist Centre). He was chosen in the Nepalese National Assembly election of 2022 and is a member of the Rashtriya Sabha as well. ==References== ==Other websites== *सदस्यहरु Category:Living people Category:Nepalese politicians
title: Bhuwan Bahadur Sunar
